data.description: Looking for a large corner lot in a no HOA community? Look no further! 3289 Pinewood Drive offers a quaint living environment with the option to do as you please. Situated on a corner lot with almost half an acre, the property provides plenty of parking, yard space, and options to make it your own. The entire property is fenced in and currently holds the main house of over 1,500 square feet, an expansive patio in the back equipped with a wet bar and metal roof, two RV's, a 980 square foot garage/work shed with two retractable garage doors, and still has plenty of yard space to use how ever you would like.As you enter the front gate you will find a long driveway leading to the carport and screened porch as well as the walkway to the front door where you will find a peaceful porch area overlooking the front landscape. The carport offers additional storage space. Upon entering through the side door, you will find a generously sized laundry room to your right, a large dine-in kitchen to your front, and the cozy family room to your left. Continuing through the family room is the formal dining area with plenty of space to gather as you please. Moving forward through the home you will find a full bathroom with a large vanity sink and shower. Additionally, all three bedrooms are located on the east wing of the home. The main bedroom is also equipped with a private, ensuite bathroom. Heading back to the screened porch you will find access to the large covered deck perfect for entertaining. There is currently a  fully functioning wet bar and refrigerator on the deck. At the other end of the deck you will find the large workshop situated in the east corner of the lot. With over 900 square feet of space, you can really use this structure or whatever you want! Last but not least, the current roof was installed in 2020 as well as the current hvac unit. This unique property offers a multitude of advantages you are not going to find anywhere else. Book a showing today to experience all that this property has to offer.
